{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cc6470a5ac","title":"随笔——失败","origin":"北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d8cf397533","index":0,"year":1957,"month":7,"day":1,"articleId":"cc6470a5ac"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"19f3f1b8ea","name":"北京大学"},{"id":"5eca061dd6","name":"谭天荣"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3df38a94f0","type":"title","text":"随笔——失败","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"e8defcac4b","type":"authors","text":"北京大学谭天荣","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"36dde8c0cc","type":"subtitle","text":"（谭天荣：北京大学物理系学生）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"cfffc9c3fa","type":"paragraph","text":"从前我养了一盆宝贵的花儿，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"81b18d4c41","type":"paragraph","text":"为容易，孕了个苞子，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"2023696aab","type":"paragraph","text":"但老是半含半吐不肯开放","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"fa7dc7da30","type":"paragraph","text":"我等得发急，硬把他剥开了，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"a819d2daa8","type":"paragraph","text":"他便一天萎似一天，萎得不像样了，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"8d021a449b","type":"paragraph","text":"如今我要他再关上不能了，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"f74f97470d","type":"paragraph","text":"我到底没有看见我要看的花！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"b2aa93052c","type":"paragraph","text":"从前我做了一个稀奇的梦，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"a6665ebb0c","type":"paragraph","text":"我光嫌他太模糊了，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"2c140520a8","type":"paragraph","text":"我满不介意，让他震破了，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"18cb732bae","type":"paragraph","text":"我醒的，直等到月落，等到天明，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"6ba23d48cf","type":"paragraph","text":"重织一个新梦既织不成，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"eaddfea477","type":"paragraph","text":"便是那个旧的也补不起来了，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"fd4cdbf55a","type":"paragraph","text":"我到底没有做好我要做好的梦！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"},{"id":"15ad549197","type":"paragraph","text":" 1957．7．1贴","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac"}],"page":{"id":"7b3b1cfca3","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"cc6470a5ac","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}